title: Wyatt Detention Center IGSA with ICE

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Rhode Island Access to Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

The current Intergovernmental Agreement or contract, including all amendments and modifications, between the Central Falls Detention Facility Corporation and the United States Marshals Services (USMS) utilized by U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) to detain noncitizens at the Donald W. Wyatt Detention Facility.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Sophia Wright

title: Public Figure Lawsuits, ROs, etc. in LA County

communications.subject: California Public Records Act Request: Public Figure Lawsuits, ROs, etc. in LA County
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

-court files from the following lawsuit: Margera et al. v. Paramount Pictures Corp. et al. (Case No.: 21STCV29254, Stanley Mosk Courthouse. filed August 9, 2021)
-court documents from the following restraining order filing: TAQUALI, DAHLIA VS TAQUALI, DIMA (CASE NUMBER: 21SMR000157; LOS ANGELES COUNTY SUPERIOR COURT. filed August 17, 2021)
-court documents from the following restraining order filing: Jevremovic v. Courville (connected to Jevremovic v. Courville 3:22-cv-04969 from District Court, D. New Jersey)
-court documents from the following restraining order filing: Linda Omar v. Courville (connected to Jevremovic v. Courville 3:22-cv-04969 from District Court, D. New Jersey)
-court documents from the following Motion for Attorney’s Fees and Costs: Case No. 23STRO05821 in LA County (connected to Jevremovic v. Courville 3:22-cv-04969 from District Court, D. New Jersey)
-court documents from the following case regarding Receiver, Protective Order, Sanctions, Gag Order, and Discovery: Case No. 24STRO00762 in LA County, happening on October 7, 2024 and October 10, 2024 (connected to Jevremovic v. Courville 3:22-cv-04969 from District Court, D. New Jersey) 
-court documents regarding the guardianship or conservatorship of Amanda Rabb. likely connected to Larry Rabb and/or Lima Jevremovic. would have happened between April 2020 and May 2021
-court documents regarding the guardianship or conservatorship of Dahlia Taquali and Dima (or Dia) Taquali. would likely involve Lima Jevremovic or Taquali
-court documents from the legal separation between Lima Jevremovic and Ivan Jevremovic. filed March 3, 2024
-business documents regarding The Last Star or The Last Star Virtual Clinic, which Lima Jevremovic founded in Los Angeles and ran between 2014 and 2019

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Nikka Singh
